---------------------------------------------------->

Encrypt:
    FileEncryption >: Decrypts all letters and numbers in a file and creates an new one in the current directory.
    String Decryption >: Decrypts a string of the users choise.

Decrypt:
    FileEncryption >: Encrypts all letters and numbers in a file and creates an new one in the current directory.
    String Decryption >: Encrypts a string of the users choise.

